♫ You walked into my life ♫

333
00:26:49,710 --> 00:26:53,080
♫ Going round and round every day ♫

334
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:56,020
♫ Try to calm my heart, near or far ♫

335
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:59,900
♫ There's an unspoken secret ♫

336
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:01,540
♫ Still constantly missing you a little ♫

337
00:27:01,540 --> 00:27:05,230
♫ But I can't let you so easily find that out ♫

338
00:27:05,230 --> 00:27:08,180
♫ Turns out you've been with me ♫

339
00:27:08,180 --> 00:27:11,320
♫ The lies gradually become tenderness ♫

340
00:27:11,320 --> 00:27:13,520
♫ Turning the strange thoughts ♫

341
00:27:13,520 --> 00:27:15,815
♫ Into real feelings ♫

342
00:27:15,815 --> 00:27:17,320
♫ Holding your hands ♫

